@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundCorner 15
[*] --> Created
Created --> Draft : approve
Draft --> Rejected : cancel
Draft : entry / log book
Rejected --> Completed : process
Completed --> Delivered : reject
Completed : entry / log book
Delivered --> Approved : reject
Delivered : entry / log book
Approved --> [*]
@enduml